    "title": "Kujitolea Kikamilifu",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "kujitolea kikamilifu",
    "language": "swh",
    "content": "<p>Neno la Kiebrania <em>kherem</em> linamaanisha &quot;limewekwa kando kwa namna maalum.&quot; Ni vigumu kutafsiri kwa sababu halina mfanano kamili katika Kiingereza cha kisasa.</p><p>Wakati Yoshua alipowaongoza Waisraeli kuchukua Kanaani, baadhi ya vitu vilihusiana na miungu ya uongo. Vitu hivi vilijulikana kama <em>kherem</em> kwa sababu vilikuwa kinyume na Bwana. Mungu aliwataka Waisraeli kuharibu vitu hivi (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh6:18\">Yoshua 6:18</a>). Walikusanya vitu vya thamani vya metali kwenye patakatifu na vikawa vitakatifu kwa Bwana (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev27:28\">Mambo ya Walawi 27:28</a>; tazama pia <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh6:19\">Yoshua 6:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh6:24\">24</a>). Wazo la &quot;kuwekwa kando maalum&quot; pia lilihusu maadui wa Israeli wakati Waisraeli walipowaangamiza wao na mali zao (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh6:17-Josh6:19\">Yoshua 6:17–19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam15:2-1Sam15:3\">1 Samweli 15:2–3</a>).</p><p>Katika Walawi <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev27:21\">Walawi 27:21</a> na <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev27:28\">28</a>, <em>kherem</em> linamaanisha kitu kilichotengwa ili kiwe cha Bwana (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num18:14\">Hesabu</a> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num18:14\">18:14</a>). Hii ilifanya kitu, ardhi, au mtu kuwa “kitakatifu sana,” kikimilikiwa daima na Bwana. Hakingeweza kukombolewa wala kurudishwa.</p><p>Wazo la kujitolea kikamilifu kupitia uharibifu kamili linaonekana katika maandiko kadhaa ya mtume Paulo:</p><ol><li><p>Kwenye <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom9:3\">Warumi 9:3</a>, Paulo alikuwa tayari kulaaniwa na Mungu ikiwa ingepelekea wokovu wa Wayahudi wenzake.</p></li><li><p>Kwenye <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal1:8-Gal1:9\">Wagalatia 1:8–9</a>, neno lile lile la Kigiriki linaelezea hatima ya wale wanaohubiri injili ya uongo.</p></li><li><p>Kwenye <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:3\">1 Wakorintho 12:3</a>, Paulo anaonya kwamba hakuna anayezungumza kwa Roho Mtakatifu anayeweza kusema, &quot;Yesu alaaniwe.&quot; Hii inamaanisha kwamba wale walio na Roho wa Mungu hawataona kifo cha Yesu msalabani kama ishara ya kukataliwa na Mungu, kama baadhi ya Wayahudi wa wakati wa Paulo walivyofanya. Badala yake, wataelewa kuwa ni kitendo cha upatanisho kwa ajili ya ubinadamu wenye dhambi, kuweka mambo sawa kati ya Mungu na watu.</p></li></ol><p><u>Sehemu za Kujifunza Zaidi</u></p><p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod22:20\">Kutoka 22:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev27:28-Lev27:29\">Walawi 27:28–29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num18:8-Num18:14\">Hesabu 18:8–14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num21:2-Num21:3\">21:2–3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut7:1-Deut7:6\">Kumbukumbu la Torati 7:1–6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut7:26\">26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut13:12-Deut13:18\">13:12–18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh6:17-Josh6:19\">Yoshua 6:17–19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh6:24\">24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh7:11-Josh7:15\">7:11–15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam15:2-1Sam15:3\">1 Samweli 15:2–3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs20:42\">1 Wafalme 20:42</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa43:26-Isa43:28\">Isaya 43:26–28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal4:5-Mal4:6\">Malaki 4:5–6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom9:3\">Warumi 9:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor16:22\">1 Wakorintho 16:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal1:8-Gal1:9\">Wagalatia 1:8–9</a></p>",
